      • createObjectName

        private javax.management.ObjectName createObjectName(java.lang.String cacheName,
                                                     java.lang.String dbName)
                                              throws java.lang.Exception
        Create an ObjectName that identifies a CacheManager management bean, or a pattern that potentially matches multiple beans.
        Parameters:
        cacheName - the name of the cache (such as PageCache), or null to create a pattern that matches all cache names
        dbName - the name of the database, or null to create a pattern that matches all database names
        Returns:
        an ObjectName suitable for looking up beans
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
